# NAME

schoolmesh\_moodleaccount\_create - Create a moodle account for a user

# SYNOPSIS

schoolmesh\_moodleaccount\_create *username* *firstname* *lastname* *password* *institution* *department* *email* 

# DESCRIPTION

Use this script to create a moodle account.
Some checks are done before the creation.

# EXAMPLES

schoolmesh_moodleaccount_create john 'John' 'Doe' ck33LmrdH_45 john.doe@example.com

